description: Roaming Fork mobile food trailer is constantly creating a rotating menu that will tantalize Charlotte's tasebuds and have you coming back for more. "Get your eat on"Some of the most satisfying food in America can now be found curbside, served out of sleek trailers or trucks retrofitted with kitchens.  The recipes found in them reinvent “truck food"....So come out and enjoy our great tasting food!
name: Roaming Fork "Bistro On Wheels"
